column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID,s.sourceType,s.class,s.subclass,p.clean,p.RA,p.DEC,p.psfMag_u,p.psfMag_g,p.psfMag_r,p.psfMag_i,p.psfMag_z FROM PhotoObj As p JOIN specObj As s ON s.bestObjID = p.ObjID JOIN PhotoTag x ON x.objID = s.objID ORDER BY s.bestObjID &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
